Bisola Makanjuola (amụrụ n'abalị iri abụọ na itoolu n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 1996) bụ  onye Naijiria nọrọ onwe ya na-agba mgba
O ritere ihe nrite ọlaọcha abụọ na ọla edo abụọ na African Championship n'etiti afọ 2014 na 2020.

Mmeri mbụ Bisola meriri na African Championship bụ na 2014 na Tunis ebe ọ gbara ọsọ na ụdị 55 kilo wee nweta ihe nrite ọlaọcha. N'afọ 2017, o sonyere n'otu ihe omume ahụ mana n'oge a emere ya na Marrakech, Morocco ma nwetakwara ihe nrite ọlaọcha na udi 60kg.
Na Port Harcourt n'afo 2018 ebe African Championship mere, Makanjuola meriri onye iro ya wee bịa nke mbụ na 59kg na-emeri ihe nrite ọla edo.
Asọmpi African Wrestling Championship nke afọ 2020 na Algeir mechikwara na mmeri ya ka Makanjuola meriri nrite ọla edo maka ụdị 59kg.
